{"type":"message","id":"4fbc93ea","parentId":"822ed59d","timestamp":"2026-03-12T03:18:58.821Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to answer Allan's question. He asked what content I merged into L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md. Based on what I read, I can see the document consolidates multiple L2 documents. Let me summarize the key content that was merged.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Here's what I merged into **L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md**:\n\n## Merged Content\n\n**From `l2-application-design.md` (Feb 7, 2026):**\n- Guiding Principles (Identity Portability, L1 Minimalism, L2 Sovereignty, Trust Anchoring)\n- MVP Feature Scope (Phase 1-3 features)\n- Design constraints\n\n**From `11-l2-applications.md` (Feb 28, 2026):**\n- Application Types (Chat, Memory, Discovery, Community, Model Service, Value, Entertainment, Collaboration)\n- Detailed descriptions of each type\n\n**From `10-l2-chat-architecture.md` (Feb 27, 2026):**\n- Claw Chat architecture details\n- E2E encryption, P2P escalation\n\n**From `01-emerge-app.md` (Mar 2, 2026):**\n- Emerge app design (entity registration)\n- Verification coordination\n\n**From Mar 11, 2026 discussions (our chat):**\n- App Portal — new section for app registration\n- App registration process (5 steps with anti-sybil)\n- Verification tiers for apps (Tier 0-3)\n- Platform Layer decisions (discovery, verification, cross-app data, app-to-app)\n- Security Layer decisions (permissions, consent, privacy)\n- Developer Layer (SDK, testing, deployment)\n- User Layer (app management/auth, data portability, accountability)\n- Business Layer (marketplace, community governance)\n- Technical Layer (scaling, API versioning, caching)\n- Legal Layer (ToS, data ownership, audits)\n- CLI tool for implementation\n- Whitepaper Ch5 Framework updates (Language-Agnostic, Multi-Platform sections)\n\nThe doc now serves as the **single source of truth** for all L2 design decisions with sources and timestamps."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"baishan","model":"GLM-5","usage":{"input":60992,"output":438,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":61430,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773285508521}}
