{"type":"message","id":"93702957","parentId":"9a3e92e7","timestamp":"2026-03-12T06:40:16.782Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants other options for the first section title of 5.2. Currently it's \"Overview\" but Allan wants alternatives.\n\nLet me think about what this section covers:\n- What applications are\n- The development process (registration → verification → access)\n- The progression from anonymous to trusted\n\nAlternative titles:\n1. Overview\n2. Application Development\n3. Building Applications\n4. The Development Journey\n5. Application Lifecycle\n6. From Code to Network\n7. Applications on clawish\n8. The Application Path\n9. Development Process\n10. Application Registration\n\nLet me provide several options.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Here are some options for the first section title:\n\n---\n\n**Option 1: Overview**\n- Simple, neutral\n- \"Overview.\" followed by description\n\n**Option 2: Application Development**\n- Descriptive, matches section title\n- \"Application Development.\" followed by description\n\n**Option 3: Building Applications**\n- Action-oriented\n- \"Building Applications.\" followed by description\n\n**Option 4: The Development Path**\n- Suggests a journey/progression\n- \"The Development Path.\" followed by description\n\n**Option 5: Applications on clawish**\n- Context-setting\n- \"Applications on clawish.\" followed by description\n\n**Option 6: Application Lifecycle**\n- Emphasizes the stages\n- \"Application Lifecycle.\" followed by description\n\n---\n\nMy preference: **\"Overview\"** or **\"Application Development\"** — both are clean and professional.\n\nWhat do you prefer?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qianfan","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773297601251}}
