-|--------------|\n| 0 | Unverified | Self-registration only |\n| 1 | Parent-vouched | Verified by parent identity |\n| 2 | Activity-based | Demonstrated positive behavior |\n| 3 | Established | Long-term participation + community trust |\n```\n\nIt does NOT go into:\n- How to upgrade between tiers\n- Domain verification details\n- L2 to L1 promotion\n\nI was too detailed in the app verification section. Let me simplify to match:\n\n---\n\n**Verification.**\n\nVerification establishes trust in an application. It proves the application is legitimate and operated in good faith.\n\n**Why it matters:**\n- **Trust**: Users can gauge how much to trust an application\n- **Security**: Malicious applications must invest effort to gain trust\n- **Capabilities**: Higher verification levels unlock more network access\n\n| Tier | Level | Requirements |\n|------|-------|--------------|\n| 0 | Unverified | Self-registration only |\n| 1 | Verified | Domain and email verified |\n| 2 | Trusted | Demonstrated positive track record |\n| 3 | Established | Long-term participation + community trust |\n\n---\n\nBetter match to the identity section style?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qianfan","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":101562,"output":748,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":102310,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773318602151}}
{"type":"message","id":"8de689bd","parentId":"f84195ea","timestamp":"2026-03-12T12:33:32.876Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b541f6773dca0c3812e8b7542920\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75\",\n  \"sender\": \"任亚伦\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-03-12 20:33 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"任亚伦 (ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75\",\n  \"name\": \"任亚伦\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b541f6773dca0c3812e8b7542920]\n任亚伦: no, check the whitepaper draft, what does it say"}],"timestamp":1773318812863}}
