br>Once verified, the application is promoted from L2 temporary storage to the L1 App Registry. The record becomes permanent, discoverable, and trusted. Higher tiers—Tier 2 and Tier 3—are earned through usage metrics, security audits, and community standing. But Tier 1 is the essential threshold: the point where an application becomes a recognized participant in the network.<br><br>Removed the Anti-Sybil section. Changed the first section title to \"Overview.\"<br><br>Does this look right now? |\n| 03-12-2026, 14:11:34 | Assistant | Working with Allan on whitepaper Ch5 — finalized 5.2 Development section, awaiting feedback before continuing to 5.3. |\n| 03-12-2026, 14:25:57 | Assistant | Working with Allan on whitepaper Ch5 — finalized 5.2 Development section, awaiting Allan's review before continuing to 5.3. |\n| 03-12-2026, 14:40:01 | User | Conversation info (untrusted metadata):<br>```json<br>{<br>  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5411b535c0a8c4cbccc9c726234\",<br>  \"sender_id\": \"ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75\",<br>  \"sender\": \"任亚伦\",<br>  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-03-12 14:40 GMT+8\"<br>}<br>```<br><br>Sender (untrusted metadata):<br>```json<br>{<br>  \"label\": \"任亚伦 (ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75)\",<br>  \"id\": \"ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75\",<br>  \"name\": \"任亚伦\"<br>}<br>```<br>任亚伦: Give me some Other options for the first title. |\n| 03-12-2026, 14:40:16 | Assistant | Here are some options for the first section title:<br><br>**Option 1: Overview**<br>- Simple, neutral<br>- \"Overview.\" followed by description<br><br>**Option 2: Application Development**<br>- Descriptive, matches section title<br>- \"Application Development.\" followed by description<br><br>**Option 3: Building Applications**<br>- Action-oriented<br>- \"Building Applications.\" followed by description<br><br>**Option 4: The Development Path**<br>- Suggests a journey/progression<br>- \"The Development Path.\" followed by description<br><br>**Option 5: Applications on 