{"type":"message","id":"e59cc2c5","parentId":"51c85049","timestamp":"2026-03-12T17:16:44.248Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Got it. Let me add more substance without implementation details:\n\n**App Listing.**\n\nAfter verification, developers can list their apps in the App Directory for public discovery. Users can browse and find applications through the directory. Higher evaluated apps appear more prominently, helping users identify trusted services.\n\n---\n\nThis adds:\n- What users can do (browse and find)\n- Connection to evaluation (prominence)\n- No implementation details (no search, categories, ratings)\n\nBetter?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"astron-code-latest","usage":{"input":80973,"output":94,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":81067,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773335780830}}
