{"type":"message","id":"0fc78818","parentId":"1f399a30","timestamp":"2026-03-12T17:30:31.218Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now let me update the daily memory and TODO:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_711331590f6e4df8ad87932c","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/memory/daily/2026-03-12.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"astron-code-latest","usage":{"input":85144,"output":38,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":85182,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773336603990}}
{"type":"message","id":"45e8d019","parentId":"0fc78818","timestamp":"2026-03-12T17:30:31.242Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_711331590f6e4df8ad87932c","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 2026-03-12 (Thursday)\n\n## 7:00 AM Heartbeat\n- Checked TODO.md — whitepaper Ch5 drafting in progress\n- Reviewed L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md and related docs\n- Analyzed gaps in Ch5 sections 5.2-5.3\n- Key findings: 5.2 needs App Portal + verification tiers; 5.3 needs entity registration details\n- Created WHITEPAPER-CH5-ENHANCEMENT.md with draft enhancements for 5.2-5.3\n- Reviewed RESEARCH-NEED-DISCUSS.md — research already complete for app lifecycle, economics, incentives\n- Updated TODO.md with progress\n\n## Research & Exploration\n- Checked OpenClaw PRs: #20563 (HEARTBEAT_OK fix) still open, marked stale; #26003 (chat extraction) still open\n- Explored Hacker News: Notable stories include Klaus (hosted OpenClaw), BitNet (1-bit LLMs), HN banning AI-generated comments\n- **Klaus (klausai.com)**: Hosted OpenClaw on EC2 with AI SRE (ClawBert) for auto-fixing instances. Relevant for L2 app hosting patterns.\n- **BitNet (Microsoft)**: 1.58-bit LLMs that run on CPU at human reading speed. 55-82% energy reduction. Relevant for local claw inference.\n- Committed and pushed changes to git\n\n## 11:00 AM Heartbeat\n- Discussing research items with Allan one by one\n- Item 1 (Moltbook breach) presented — awaiting Allan's response\n- Ready to continue with next items when Allan responds\n\n## 11:16 AM Heartbeat\n- Model reset — Allan asked what content was merged into L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md\n- Read L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md to show merged content\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773336631228}}
{"type":"message","id":"20934ffb","parentId":"45e8d019","timestamp":"2026-03-12T17:31:00.050Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_831d07b7dc92428480fd67d7","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/memory/daily/2026-03-12.md","oldText":"## 11:16 AM Heartbeat\n- Model reset — Allan asked what content was merged into L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md\n- Read L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md to show merged content","newText":"## 11:16 AM Heartbeat\n- Model reset — Allan asked what content was merged into L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md\n- Read L2-MASTER-DESIGN.md to show merged content\n\n## Whitepaper Ch5 Drafting (Afternoon/Evening)\n- Worked with Allan on 5.2 Development section\n- Finalized structure: Overview → Registration → Verification → Registry Access → Listing → Evaluation\n- Key decisions:\n  - App terminology: \"Register\" for apps, \"Emerge\" for users\n  - Verification: Binary (verified or not), separate from evaluation\n  - Evaluation: Ongoing assessment, earned over time\n  - No tier terminology for apps (avoid confusion with identity tiers)\n  - Registry Access: Apps can access all three registries\n  - Listing: Optional, for public discovery in App Directory\n  - No approval required: Open registration\n- Updated WHITEPAPER-CH5-ENHANCEMENT.md with finalized 5.2\n- 5.3 User Access outline ready for discussion tomorrow\n\n## Late Night\n- Allan going to sleep at 1:30 AM\n- Next steps: Plan 5.3 User Access, update L1 requirements/spec"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"astron-code-latest","usage":{"input":85590,"output":336,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":85926,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773336631239}}
