{"type":"message","id":"5f2e1862","parentId":"0d4d9202","timestamp":"2026-03-12T17:33:52.524Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b541bc131b4a0c2acb5e7cd26d0e\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75\",\n  \"sender\": \"任亚伦\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-03-13 01:33 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"任亚伦 (ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75\",\n  \"name\": \"任亚伦\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b541bc131b4a0c2acb5e7cd26d0e]\n任亚伦: No update the white paper draft 0307"}],"timestamp":1773336832510}}
